==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water flea
<hw>Wa"ter flea`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of
numerous species of small aquatic Entomostraca belonging to the genera
<gen>Cyclops</gen>, <gen>Daphnia</gen>, etc; -- so called because they
swim with sudden leaps, or starts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waterflood</ent>⟦br⟧
